  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Raising rail fares and putting people in crisis is not acceptable - Railway Station Master's Association",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sumedha Somaratna, President of the Railway Station Principals Association, said that although there are many ways to increase the income of the Sri Lanka Railway Department, it is not acceptable to increase the train fare only and put the public in crisis.",
        "He further mentioned that although there is a need to increase the railway transport fares, we cannot accept the rate at which the transport fares have been increased.",
        "There is not enough time to inform the general public about the revision of transport and packages services, and one day is not enough for account registration and related work at railway stations. Therefore, it would be better to implement the new railway transport tariff from the first day of the coming year, said the President of Railway Station Principals Association.",
        "Minister Bandula Gunawardena issued a gazette notification for the revision of rail fares effective from the 22nd of this month on the 21st.",
        "In this situation, the Railway Station Principal Association has informed the General Manager of the Sri Lanka Railway Department through a written document stating that there is not enough time to inform the passengers about the fare revision and to give time to make the railway station account records."
      ],
